<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-3945] Statically imported closure field is not resolved</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-3945</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;create a class with code:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;A {
  def x = {print &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;x is called&apos;&lt;/span&gt;}
} 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and a script:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; A.x

x()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This script fails with MethodMissingException.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But script:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; A.x

def a = x;
a()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;works well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
